@startuml rehearse

' Rehearse is the verification path. It opens from the shared pipeline (drawn in
' pipeline.puml) with the one twist that makes a Rehearsal Set: the
' Worktree substitutes for its Owning Repo's Session Clone, so the pending
' Contribution is the one integrated. Rehearse installs a Rehearsal Installation
' (a single self-contained root that mirrors the Host's Claude state so the smoke
' is faithful) and never touches the Host.

!include elements.puml

title Ringmaster: Rehearse (verification path)

left to right direction

actor "David" as david

rectangle "Pipeline\n(Survey → Build → Install)" as pipeline <<phase>>

david    --> pipeline : ""ringmaster stage <worktree>""
worktree --> pipeline : substitutes its Owning Repo's\nSession Clone
pipeline --> staged   : place to a single root,\n+ mirror host state

' Drop UL elements declared in elements.puml but not referenced here, so the
' rendered SVG carries no orphan boxes.
remove @unlinked

@enduml
